I write to express my deep remorse and formally plead guilty to the charge of careless driving. I accept full responsibility for my actions and the devastating consequences that resulted from my reckless behavior.

On the day in question, I was rushing to the airport to pick up my family members. Unfortunately, due to my lateness, I made the poor decision to drive aggressively and exceed the speed limit. I also made the grave mistake of answering a text message while driving, which caused me to lose focus and collide with a guardrail.

In hindsight, I deeply regret my actions and acknowledge the danger I posed not only to myself, but also to others on the road. The impact of this incident has made me realize the gravity of such reckless behavior.

