In conclusion, I humbly accept my guilt in the charge of careless driving and sincerely apologize for any harm caused. I understand the consequences of my actions and assure you that I have learned from this experience. I kindly request the court's leniency, taking into consideration my clean record and involvement in charitable activities. Thank you for your time and consideration.

Sincerely,

Charlotte Porter
